Vale CEO Ferreira Plans to Boost Workforce in 2012, Folha Says

-- B y   L a u r a   P r i c e
-- 
2011-10-16T13:31:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-16/vale-ceo-to-boost-workforce-in-2012-build-mine-in-angola-folha-reports.html
Vale SA (VALE3)  plans to increase its
workforce next year to “much more” than the current 126,000
employees, Folha de S. Paulo reported, citing Chief Executive
Officer Murilo Ferreira.  The Brazilian iron-ore producer will determine its hiring
plan by the end of this month, the newspaper said, citing
Ferreira. Vale also plans to build mines in Angola and  Guinea ,
Folha cited Ferreira as saying.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Laura Price at 
 lprice3@bloomberg.net  